---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10);
---
<Base title="Terms" description="Terms of use for strmanuals.com. Paid PDFs, instant download, 14-day refund." path="/terms">
  <section class="container-page py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto measure">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mb-3">Terms.</h1>
      <p class="text-sm price-mono mb-10" style="color: var(--color-mute);">Last updated <time datetime={today}>{today}</time></p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">What you're buying</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        Each manual is a downloadable PDF, watermarked at the time of purchase. You
        receive a single-user license: download for personal reference, do not
        redistribute, do not resell. Bundles and companion workbooks have the same
        terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Not professional advice</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        Manuals categorized as <em>tax</em> or <em>legal</em> are plain-English
        education, not professional advice. Every taxpayer and every jurisdiction
        is different. Consult a CPA or attorney before making filings, payments,
        or decisions based on a manual's content. We disclaim liability for
        actions taken on the strength of any manual.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Refunds</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        14 days, no questions. See <a href="/refund">/refund</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        Free updates within the same major version (v1 → v1.x). Major-version
        upgrades (v1 → v2) are sold separately at a discount for existing buyers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        We may update these terms. Material changes will be reflected by an
        updated "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
